Qpon: Your Go-To App for Daily Deals in Indonesia

Qpon is Indonesia's trusted lifestyle discount app, helping you discover the best vouchers and coupons for food, drinks, shopping, entertainment, and daily essentials. Save more every day with exclusive deals from top brands across Indonesia.

Whether you're craving coffee at Kopi Kenangan, grabbing a meal at McDonald's, Pizza Hut, or HokBen, or shopping daily at Alfamart and Indomaret, Qpon helps you enjoy more and spend less. Planning a movie night? Find cheaper cinema tickets and snacks with Qpon. From dining and shopping to entertainment and everyday needs, Qpon makes every purchase more valuable.

[Qpon Key Features]
Welcome Bonus for New Users
Exclusive deals and extra savings on your first order.

Hidden Gem Recommendations
Discover high-quality shops across multiple categories carefully selected to meet your lifestyle needs.

Featured Short Videos
Explore immersive videos from trending stores and unlock hidden deals instantly with just one tap.

Tried It? Rate It!
Use the new review feature to share your go-to spots and local tips. Share your experience and help build a more trusted food scene in Indonesia!

Restaurant Discount Vouchers
Save up to 50% on popular food brands including Chinese, Japanese, Korean, Western cuisine, coffee, desserts, and convenience store items.

Entertainment Deals
Find great discounts for cinemas like XXI and save on your favorite entertainment experiences anytime, anywhere.


[Why Choose Qpon]
Unbeatable Flash Sales
Join daily flash sales starting at 7AM, featuring special offers from McDonald's, Kopi Kenangan, Alfamart, Indomaret, and more.

All-in-One Convenience
Find the best deals for dining, shopping, and entertainment all in one app, accessible anytime, anywhere.

Location-Based Offers
Discover deals nearby for malls, restaurants, and coffee shops based on your location—perfect for spontaneous plans or daily routines.

Affordable Entertainment
Save on movie tickets, snacks, and weekend outings with exclusive entertainment discounts.

Discover Local Hidden Gems
Browse curated shop lists and short videos to easily find the best local spots wherever you are.

Don't miss out on the best shops
Sharing real experiences, creating a map of the city's flavours, and interacting with each other!

[About Qpon]
Qpon is a fast-growing lifestyle deals platform in Indonesia, offering daily vouchers, coupons, and discounts to make your everyday life easier and more affordable.
Learn more at: www.qpon.id/home

Download now and start saving!


[Customer Service]
Need assistance? Contact us via:
WhatsApp Business: +62 8159 787878

[Follow Us on Social Media]
Instagram: @qpon.indonesia
TikTok: @qpon.indonesia
Facebook: @qpon.indonesia

Fore Coffee is the first retail coffee startup that combines coffee with technology. Fore Coffee is committed to producing premium-quality coffee at affordable prices.


Through this application, you can purchase coffee quickly, easily, and skip the queue. Everything is customizable according to your preferences! Download now and experience a new way of enjoying coffee!

DELIVERY WITHIN 15 MINUTES 
Astro guarantees fast delivery within 15 minutes to fulfill your daily needs. 
1500+ Product Assortments, including: 
- Fruits & Veggies
- Dairy & Poultry
- Meat & Seafood
- Pastry
- Home Cleaning Supplies
- Stationary 
- Snacks & Ice Cream
- Over the Counter Medicine
-  and many more!

AVAILABLE 24/7 (in compliance with the goverment regulations)
Whenever or wherever you are we're ready to serve you anytime you need

HOW DOES IT WORK?
1. Download Astro Application
2. Fill in your delivery address
3. Browse your favorite produts and add to cart
4. Checkout & pay in 1 page
5. Your order will be delivered to your doorstep within 15 minutes

AVAILABLE PAYMENT METHODS
1. E-wallet such as GoPay, Ovo, ShopeePay, Dana, LinkAja
2. Virtual Accounts: BCA, BRI, BNI, Mandiri, Permata
3. Credit card / Debit Card: Visa, Mastercard, JCB

So what are you waiting for ? Download Astro right now and experience magical delivery services within 15 minutes!

Great Coffee. No Queue. Just Try.

Kopi Kenangan App helps you to save time in getting that high quality coffee everyday. With some additional time (and coffee), you can finish your tasks earlier, have more family time, learn new skills on the internet, or work on a new project. 

Use Kopi Kenangan App to pre-order your favourite coffee in advance and you will be notified once your order is ready. No more queueing with anxiety, stress and uncertainty!


LOCATE NEAREST OUTLET
- With more than 800 outlets across Indonesia, the app will help you find the most convenient outlet for you to order.
- Integrated to your maps for easy direction.
- View operational hours of different outlets.


CUSTOM YOUR ORDER
- We have several different brands*, offering golden, soft-as-a-pillow bread (Cerita Roti), the most tender fried chicken (Chigo!), or Soft Cookies (Kenangan Manis) to complement your coffee experience with Kopi Kenangan.
- Custom each item according to your preference (customizable temperature, size, sugar, ice, toppings, or variants)... everything through the app.


PRE-ORDER
- Set your preferred pickup time in the app to match your busy schedule.
- Your barista will prepare closer to the pickup time to ensure your order is always fresh when you receive it.


CASHLESS PAYMENTS
- Minimize contact and save more time with broad payment options (e-wallets, debit card, credit card) available in the app.


GET NOTIFIED REAL TIME
- For each order progress, you will be notified real time through the app.
- Once your order is ready, you can just go to the outlet to grab the item on the special pickup area (no queue).


COLLECT POINTS
- Collect "Hearts" Points in every in-app order to unlock five (5) membership levels.
- Enjoy more benefits as you go higher.


EXCLUSIVE APP PROMO
- Enjoy app-only offerings. Limited quota

*only available in selected outlets

Get rewarded for skipping the queue!

You can now have the Domino’s store in the palm of your hand with the Domino’s Indonesia iPhone App and order your favourite pizza!

Flick through our menu, register or order as a guest, customize your pizza, select your order, choose carry out or delivery and place your order. It is as simple as that! And with our Pizza Tracker you will be able to easily track when your order will be ready in the store or when it is going to arrive at your front door! You can even place an advanced time order for a future date or time, so you can order your favourite pizza for today, tomorrow or the day after tomorrow!

The Domino’s iPhone Mobile App is filled with exciting pizza offers and discounts from our tempting menu for you to choose from. 

This is one App you MUST have on your iPhone!

This application is only valid for ordering in Indonesia only.The free delivery promise of 30 minutes guarantee is applicable for all orders placed through this Mobile Application. For more details please refer to the Terms & Conditions, Terms of Use and Privacy Policy information listed in this application. Terms & Conditions apply.

Get the best of Starbucks® Rewards right at your fingertips. The Starbucks® Indonesia app is a convenient way to get better deals, order ahead and be handsomely rewarded for being a member. Rewards are mainly converted from your collected Stars to earn free food and beverages on your purchases.

Earn Stars However You Pay
Join Starbucks® Rewards and unlock exclusive benefits while earning Stars with every purchase.
Earn 1 Star for every Rp.6.000, - spent with your Starbucks Card balance, or 1 Star for every Rp.12,000, - spent using other method of payment (debit / credit / cash / etc.). Earn Stars even quicker with Double Star Days, Bonus Star programs and unique Member offers.

Track your Stars Conversion & Rewards
Collect your Stars, select, and redeem your preferred Rewards of free drinks, food and more. Starbucks® Rewards members can now also track converted Stars and redeemed Rewards in the app.

Be the first to be Informed on anything Starbucks Indonesia
Explore the app with updated news, highlights, and promotions available in Starbucks Indonesia.

Mobile Order & Pay
The Starbucks Indonesia app provides you with a faster, easier and convenient way to seamlessly order ahead, pay and customize your favorites for pickup in our selected participating stores without waiting in line.
With Mobile Order & Pay you are now also able to earn and collect Stars for every purchase and redeem special offers, food, and beverages with your Rewards.

Manage Starbucks Cards
Check your Starbucks Card balance; add money with the online Top-Up feature in the app, view past purchases, add / remove card designs in your account.

Seamless Top Up
Top-Up or reload your card balance online using a Virtual Account with selected m-banking services. Static VA is currently available for m-BCA users for a better reload experience, where at any time, you can Top-Up directly and seamlessly from the mobile banking app without going through the Top-Up process in our Starbucks Indonesia app.

Find a Store
See stores near you, get directions, hours, and view store amenities before you make the trip.

Refer a Friend
Share the joy and benefits with your friends that have not joined the Starbucks® Rewards membership program. Copy your referral code from your profile, share it with a friend, fill in the referral code box in the registration page, and get rewards for every successful referral. The more you share, the more rewards you get!

Enjoy a better way of doing business.
Two simple steps to become a Grab merchant-partner:

1. Sign up your business first with our sales team.

2. After signing up, download this app to enjoy a better way of doing business.

If you want to create more opportunities for business growth, this mobile app will support you. It offers delivery and a secure cashless payment option to millions of consumers. Now who doesn’t want that?

Being a Grab merchant-partner means enjoying more options
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Expand your business beyond the breakfast-lunch-dinner crowd or your in-store customers. GrabFood allows you to deliver meals when hunger strikes at any time of the day. GrabMart helps you reach out to more customers and make grocery deliveries straight to their homes. 

The GrabMerchant app makes your online business more seamless
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
If you’re running a food delivery service or even a grocery store, this app manages your processes efficiently – so you can focus on what you do best.

Manage orders easily
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Check all the orders coming into your restaurant or store and track the ones that are being fulfilled, straight from your device. 

Grow your sales online
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Offer discounts to convert them into loyal customers. Advertise within the app to get more orders.

Get better insights
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A good seller makes better business decisions, supported by data and store performance. See what’s working right for you, so you can focus your efforts to make more sales.

Learn with GrabAcademy
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Running a restaurant or a shop isn’t easy. So we’re making it easier for you with lessons on how to improve your performance. 

Enable secure payments
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Going cashless helps both you and your customers. No matter what you’re selling on the app, you can now track and trace where your money comes and goes, while giving your customers the flexibility to pay faster and safer.

Manage your storefront
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Create, upload and update your menu or catalogue to stand out from the crowd.

Manage employees access
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Create designated profiles for different members of your team.


Some features are only available in selected markets.

To learn more about the information used in our mobile app, including our interest-based advertising and cross-device tracking, or to exercise certain opt-out choices you may have, please refer to our Privacy Policy.

Privacy Policy : www.grab.com/privacy
Open Source Software Attributions: www.grb.to/oss-attributions

Now Available: the JCO Indonesia mobile ordering app! Our JCO delivery service app allows customers in Indonesia to place orders via IOS devices. Ordering JCO is now easier with a wide selection of our best-selling donuts, JCoffee, and JCool products. You can order from the safety of your own home or office without any hassle! We are here to support your WFH days!

Please always update JCO Apps to get our latest promotions.
